### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Authenticate to Get Token
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "analista@seplag.rj.gov.br",
    "password": "orcamento@2026"
}

### Save the Token from the Response Body
@jwtToken = {{loginRequest.response.body.*}}

### 2. Access a Protected Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teste HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json